{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Add languages to the UK Shortage Occupation List for Skilled Worker visa",
        "additional_details": "Many of our clients within the STEM sectors require native foreign language skills for international roles based in the UK.\r\n\r\nAs examples:\r\nLead Development Representatives for a Cyber Security company\r\nResearch Executives for a Scientific Market Research company\r\n \r\nThese roles are typically filled by international graduates, but they would be unable to continue after the end of their Post-Study Work visa as proficient language skills are omitted from the List for a Skilled Worker visa.",
        "background": "As a recruitment business working in the STEM (Scientific, Technology, Engineering & Manufacturing) sectors, we believe that proficient language skills should be added to the UK Shortage Occupation List for obtaining a Skilled Work visa.",
